<h4>Architecture Firm History</h4>
<p>
Komatsu Architecture, established in Fort Worth in 1959 by Albert S. Komatsu, is a second-generation family owned professional design organization.  Our firm is skilled in providing architectural, interior design, programming, historic preservation, master planning and related services to local, state, national and international clients.  We are dedicated to a standard of excellence in every project we undertake. To this end, we assemble a team with the talents to analyze and define problems, develop solutions, and coordinate and manage the planning and construction process.  It is a source of continued pride that new and previous clients choose Komatsu for demanding projects, seeking our services when they need exceptional creativity, thoughtful planning and strong management control.
</p>
</div>
